<LP>
   HOUSTON -- Texas Meridian Resources Ltd., a master limited
partnership, said it plans to reorganize into a corporate
entity and that in conjunction with the restructuring,
Manufacturers Hanover Trust Co. will increase the oil and gas
concern's existing revolving credit line to $32.5 million
plus a new subordinated note in the amount of $5 million.
</LP>
